wordlist.description: These pairs of homophones sound the same but have different meanings and spellings. A clue is given after the bleep to distinguish them. The crossword (sentence) games put them into context and help students build up a visual memory for which spelling goes with which meaning. The Extended sample tab is rebuilt each time it is selected and draws from a very extensive list of homophones.
wordlist.name: homophones - see 'More Words'
